title: CPaaS SDK for business communication solutions | Rainbow
metaDescription: Add chat, conference, real time collaboration and communication (PBX, VoIP, P2P) capabilities, bots and more to your business applications.
mainHtml:
Documentation

Changelog

SDK.Common for C#

[2.6.18-LTS] - 2024-07-01

Changed

  • Colors list used to create Avatars has been changed.
  • .Net 6.0 as target plateform has been removed (obsolete). .Net Std 2.0, 2.1 and .Net 8.0 are still in targets platform.

[2.6.17-LTS] - 2024-05-27

Added

  • ImageTools: GetSvgAsStringFromResourceName()
  • New SVG files added (528 in total)

[2.6.16-LTS] - 2024-03-19

Fixed

  • The avatar of a bubble based on the avatars of its members will no longer contain the initials of one or more of these members

Changed

  • Breaking GetBitmapFromSvgResourceName() and GetBitmapFromSvgFile(): No longer return a square image but respect the SVG layout. A width parameter replaces the old size parameter. The height is automatically calculated.
  • Avatars: now use logger prefix set in Rainbow.Application to create folder where Avatars are stored - so by default it will be Path.Combine(application.GetIniPathFolder(), "Resources", $"{prefix}Avatars")
  • Files: now use logger prefix set in Rainbow.Application to create folder where Files are stored - so by default it will be Path.Combine(application.GetIniPathFolder(), "Resources", $"{prefix}Files")
  • Update all labels for 22 languages
  • Upgrade package SkiaSharp to 2.88.7 from 2.88.6 (since a rollback of dependencies used in this package has been done in this new version)
  • Use Svg.Skia 1.0.0.13 instead of SkiaSharp.Svg 1.60.0 to allow to manage more type of SVG

Added

  • Include more than 500 SVG (before ~60 SVG)

[2.6.15-LTS] - 2024-01-15

Added

  • Add .Net 8.0 as target plateform (.Net Std 2.0, 2.1 and .Net 6.0 are still in targets platform) .Net 6.0 target platform will be removed in April.

Changed

  • Upgrade dependency package SkiaSharp to 2.88.6 from 2.80.3 (due to high security vulnerability)

[2.6.14-LTS] - 2023-09-05

Changed

  • Technical delivery to use SDK C# (Core) v2.6.18

[2.6.13] - LTS - 2023-07-07

  • .Net Core App 3.1 is no more targetted (already deprecated by Microsoft).
  • .Net Standardd 2.0 / 2.1 and .Net 6.0 are still targetted

[2.6.12] - LTS - 2023-05-26

  • Dependency no more used: Newtonsoft.Json

  • Update all labels to the most recent version

[2.6.11] - LTS - 2023-05-03

  • Technical delivery due to SDK (core) updates

[2.6.10] - LTS - 2022-07-12

  • Technical delivery to modify the validity date of the SDK

[2.6.9] - LTS - 2022-05-10

  • Enriched documentation

  • Technical delivery to modify the validity date of the SDK

[2.6.8] - LTS - 2022-08-23

Enhancements

It's now possible to log on different files if several instance of the SDK (Core) is used in sametime (for example if you use several bots in the same process).

You need to set to the new parameter loggerPrefix a different value for each instance when Rainbow.Application object is created. You also need to use a different configuration file for your logger. See the online documentation for more details.

In consequence the way to create these services have changed: Avatars, Languages and ImageTools:


// Create Rainbow.Application - here with a logger prefix
String prefix = "BOT01_"; // This can be null or empty if you don't need it
var application = new Rainbow.Application(loggerPrefix: prefix);

// -------------------------------------------------

// Before Avatars service was created like this:
var avatars = Rainbow.Common.Avatars.Instance;
avatars.SetApplication(application);

// Now we use this to create Avatars service:
var avatars = Rainbow.Common.Avatars.CreateInstance(application);

// -------------------------------------------------

// Before Languages service was created like this:
var languages = Rainbow.Common.Languages.Instance;

// Now we use this to create Languages service:
var languages = Rainbow.Common.Languages.CreateInstance(application);

// -------------------------------------------------

// Before ImageTools service was composed of only static methods. Now you need to create it before to use any methods
var imageTools = Rainbow.Common.ImageTools.CreateInstance(application);

No update since last LTS version - Increase release versions to be consistent with other packages SDK (core)

No update since last STS version - Increase release versions to be consistent with other packages SDK (core)

[2.5.2] - STS - 2021-10-20

Avatars service: updated

  • PeerAvatarUpdated: fix Event could be raised just before the avatar file was saved locally

[2.5.1] - STS - 2021-09-29

Deprecated events removed:

  • Events removed: ContactAvatarUpdated, BubbleAvatarUpdated
  • Use instead event: PeerAvatarUpdated

[2.5.0] - LTS - 2021-09-08

API update in details:

Files service: updated

  • GetFolderPathForFilesStorage: new Return the folder path where files are stored by this service
  • GetFolderPathForThumbnailsStorage: new Return the folder path where file thumbnails are stored by this service

[2.4.0] - LTS - 2021-08-12

Dependency

Bump SkiaSharp package to 2.80.3 from 2.80.2

Avatar service:

Fix: To know if the Avatar stored locally was more recent the property 'CreationTimeUtc' was used. Now 'LastWriteTimeUtc' is use instead.

Languages service:

The current language of the device is now used as default language (instead of "en") if this service has a correct dictionary associated. (using internally CultureInfo.CurrentUICulture.TwoLetterISOLanguageName)

If several dictionaries are found (for example for Portuguese we have two dictionaries "pt-BR" and "pt-PT") the first one found is used by default.

Files service:

Fix: Don't increase size of thumbnails or image files which are smaller than MaxThumbnailWidth and/or MaxThumbnailHeight

ImageTools library:

  • Add 13 new Svg as resources in this library

API update in details:

Avatars service: updated

  • PeerAvatarUpdated: new Event raised when a peer avatar is updated
  • BubbleAvatarUpdated: deprecated Use instead PeerAvatarUpdated event
  • ContactAvatarUpdated: deprecated Use instead PeerAvatarUpdated event

Languages service: updated

  • GetLanguageIdListAccordingDeviceLanguage: new List available "languageId" according the device language. (using internally CultureInfo.CurrentUICulture.TwoLetterISOLanguageName). For example, using "pt", two "languageId" are returned "pt-BR" and "pt-PT". For "en" only one is returned: "en".
  • GetLabel(labelKey, subtituteKey, subtituteValue): new Get the specified label for the current language. In the label itself, substite a key by a value.

Files service: updated

  • FileDescriptorNotAvailable: new Event raised when a FileDescriptor is no more available: the assocatied file has been deleted or is no more accessible (no more viewer for example)
  • IsFileDescriptorNotAvailable: new To kwon if a FileDescriptor is no more available: the assocatied file has been deleted or is no more accessible (no more viewer for example)

[2.2.0] - LTS - 2021-06-09

ImageTools libray:

  • Add 10 new Svg as resources in this library

[2.1.0] - LTS - 2021-05-24

Files service: (new)

This service permits to facilitate the download of files descriptor, files thumbnail and files.

When a file descriptor has been downloaded:

  • if authorized, a thumbnail is automatically downloaded too.
  • if authorized and orignal file size enough smaller, the original image file is automatically downloaded instead of its thumbnail.

Once downloaded, thumbnails are automatically resized based on the max height or max width specified.

Thumbnails and originals files are stored in the specified folder.

Avatars service:

  • Bubble avatar created with theirs members now use first creator, then moderators then members. Avoid current user if possible
  • Enhance download management on network trouble or on incorrect server responses

ImageTools library:

  • Add 14 new Svg as resources in this library

API update in details:

Avatars service: updated

  • AddUnknownContactToPoolById() new - To add contact avatar (by Id) to the download pool
  • AddUnknownContactToPoolByJid() new - To add contact avatar (by Jid) to the download pool
  • GetTheoricContactAvatarPath new - Returns the path of the contact Avatar according it's type only whatever the status of this avatar download.
  • GetTheoricBubbleAvatarPath updated - Returns the path of the bubble Avatar according it's type only whatever the status of this avatar download.
  • BubbleAvatarUpdated updated - This event is now raised only when all avatars members, used to create bubble avatar, are all downloaded.

Files service: new

Events

  • FileDescriptorAvailable new - Event raised when a FileDescriptor is available
  • ThumbnailAvailable new - Event raised when a thumbnail has been downloaded successfully and is available

Properties

  • AllowAutomaticThumbnailDownload new - To allow / disallow automatic thumbnail download - False by default
  • AllowFileDescriptorDownload new - To allow / disallow file descriptor download - True by default
  • AutomaticDownloadLimitSizeForImages new - To download original image and not thumbnail if its size is smaller than this property (in bytes) - 250 by default.
  • MaxThumbnailHeight new - Thumbnail will be resized automatically if its height is greater than this property - 200 by default
  • MaxThumbnailWidth new - Thumbnail will be resized automatically if its width is greater than this property - 200 by default

Methods

  • AskFileDescriptorDownload(conversationId, fileDescriptorId) new - To ask the download of a file descriptor in a conversation.
  • AskThumbnailDownload(fileDescriptorId) new - To ask the download of a thumbnail. The file descriptor must be available first.
  • GetAllConversationIdByFilesDescriptorIdFromCache() new - Get a dictionary of conversation id indexed by file descriptor id stored in the cache
  • GetAllFilesDescriptorFromCache() new - Get FileDescriptor object using fileDescriptorId.
  • GetConversationIdByFileDescriptorId(fileDescriptorId) new - To get the conversation Id related to the specified file descriptor Id.
  • GetFileDescriptor(fileDescriptorId) new - Get FileDescriptor object using fileDescriptorId.
  • GetFullFilePath(fileDescriptorId) new - Get in a dictionary (by file descriptor id) all files descriptor stored in cache
  • GetThumbnailFullFilePath(fileDescriptorId) new - Get file path to the thumbnail using file descriptor Id.
  • IsThumbnailFileAvailable(conversationId, fileDescriptorId, fileName) new - To know if thumbnail file is available
  • SetApplication(application) new - To set Rainbow Application object
  • SetDensity(density) new - Set the density used by the current device in order to resize correctly thumbnail - 1 by default
  • SetFolderPath(folderPath) new - Set folder path where thumbnails and files will be stored

ImageTools library: updated

  • GetImageSize() new - To get image size (using file path, SKImage or SKBitmap)

[2.0.0] - LTS Beta - 2021-04-23

  • Avoid some crash when creating SVG object with incorrect data or invalid file path

[0.0.1.0] - 2021-04-01

Avatars service: updated Default avatar size is now 100 (no more 60)

ImageTools library: updated

Methods

  • GetSvgResourceNameList() new - Get list of Svg available as resource (10 for the moment)
  • GetSvgFromResourceName(resourceName) new - Get Svg object using the specified resource name
  • GetBitmapFromSvgResourceName(resourceName, size, backgroundColor, color) new - Create bitmap from Svg using the specified background color and pen color
  • GetBitmapFromSvgResourceName(resourceName, size, backgroundColor, colorTransformations) new - - Create bitmap from Svg using the specified background color and list of color to use form original colors

Languages service: new This service permits to get labels in the specified language (22 in total). By default 'en' is used as language Id.

Events

  • LanguageChanged new - Raised when the language has been changed

Properties

  • Instance new - To get isntance of thi service

Methods

  • GetLabel(key) new - To get the label using the specified key
  • GetLabels() new - To get all lables available
  • GetLanguage() new - To get language id currently used
  • GetLanguagesList() new - To get list of languages supported
  • SetLanguage(languageId) new - To set the language to use (using its id)

[0.0.0.1-alpha] - 2021-03-11

Avatars service: new

Events

  • BubbleAvatarUpdated new - Raised when a Bubble avatar as been updated
  • ContactAvatarUpdated new - Raised when a Contact avatar as been updated

Methods

  • AddInDownloadPoolAllAvatarsFromBubblesStoredInCache() new - Download (one by one) and if it's not already done, all avatars of bubbles stored in the cache of Bubbles service.
  • AddInDownloadPoolAllAvatarsFromContactsStoredInCache() new - Download (one by one) and if it's not already done, all avatars of contacts stored in the cache of Contacts service.
  • AllowAvatarDownload(value) new - To allow avatar download. Can be set / unset at any time to stop / start avatars download.
  • AllowToAskInfoAboutUnknowBubble(value) new - To allow this service to ask server info automatically (to get name, members, avatar) if an unknown bubble is found.
  • AllowToAskInfoForUnknownContact(value) new - To allow this service to ask server info automatically (to get displaynae, initials and avatar) if an unknown contact is found.
  • GetAvatarsFolderPath(type, forContact) new - Return the path used to store avatar accoring the AvatarType specified
  • GetBubbleAvatarPath(bubbleId, avatarType) new - Return the Bubble Avatar path. A path to an valid image is always returned.
  • GetColorFromDisplayName(displayName) new - Return a Hex String color using the display name
  • GetContactAvatarPath(contactId, avatarType) new - Return the Contact Avatar path. A path to an valid image is always returned.
  • GetDarkerColorFromDisplayName(displayName) new - Return a Hex String color (darker) using the display name
  • GetUnknwonAvatarFilePath new - Get the path to the avatar used for unknwon contact
  • Initialize() new - Initialize this service.
  • SetApplication(application) new - To specify the Rainbow Application service
  • SetAvatarSize(value, avatarType) new - Set avatar size according its type. (without taking into account density)
  • SetDensity(density) new - According the device / the context, the pixel density is note equals to 1 (default value)
  • SetFolderPathUsedToStoreAvatars(path) new - Set folder path where avatars will be stored
  • SetTextColor(hexColor) new - Set color of the text to create Avatar using initials (#FFFFFF by default)
  • SetTextHeightSize(size) new - Set text height (in px - without taking into account density) which will be used to create avatar using initials

ImageTools: new

  • ArcPartOfSquareBitmap(srcBitmap, partNumber, nbParts, antiAliasing) new - Get an Arc part of the specified bitmap
  • CopyBitmap(bitmap) new - Copy the specified bitmap
  • CreateBitmap(width, height, hexColor) new - Create a bitmap
  • CreateCircleBitmap(size, circleHexColor, antiAliasing) new - Create a circle bitmap
  • DegreeToRadian(angle) new - Convert degree to radian
  • DrawBitmapOnAnotherOne(srcBitmap, dstBitmap, xDest, yDest) new - Draw a bitmap on another one
  • DrawBitmapOnAnotherOne(srcBitmap, dstBitmap, xDest, yDest, width, height, maintainRatio, quality) new - Draw a bitmap on another one
  • GetBitmapFromFile(filePath) new - Get a bitmap from file
  • GetBitmapFromImage(image) new - Get an bitmap from image
  • GetImageFromBitmap(bitmap) new - Get an image from bitmap
  • GetImageFromFile(filePath) new - Get an image from file
  • GetSizeUsingDensity(size) new - Get size (in px) according density
  • GetStreamFromBitmap(bitmap) new - Get stream from bitmap
  • GetStreamFromImage(image) new - Get stream from image
  • OvalBitmap(srcBitmap, antiAliasing) new - Create oval image from the specified bitmap
  • SaveBitmapToFile(bitmap, filePath, format, quality) new - Save bitmap to file
  • SaveImageToFile(image, filePath, format, quality) new - Save image to file
  • ScaleAndSquareBitmap(srcBitmap, size, maintainRatio, quality) new - Scale and square specified bitmap
  • ScaleBitmap(srcBitmap, imgWidth, imgHeight, maintainRatio, quality) new - Scale specified bitmap
  • SetArcPartInfo(color, strokeWidth) new - Set color and stroke width use to create arc part of an bitmap
  • SetDensity(density) new - Set density
  • TranslateBitmap(srcBitmap, x, y) new - Translate a bitmap
  • WriteCenteredTextToBitmap(bitmap, text, textColor, textHeight, antiAliasing) new - Write centered text (horizontally and vertically) on the specified bitmap
